                  <p class="card-text mt-4">
                    【喝酒網門市春節營業時間】</br>
                    ．除夕：各門市營業至晚上6點</br>
                    ．初一－初三：各門市公休</br>
                    ．初四：恢復正常營業時間</br></br>
                    如有疑問，歡迎加入官方LINE@，將有客服人員協助您處理～喝酒網在此預祝各位新年快樂！龍年行大運，好運巄總來🐲🧧🧨
                  </p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-end mb-2 me-2 "><small class="text-muted">2024/01/25</small></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 消息2 -->
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="card mx-5">
            <div class="row g-1">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <a class="enlarge-img" href="/images/index/news/202401_02.png" title="春節營業時間">
                  <img src="/images/index/news/202401_02.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="春節營業時間">
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h2 class="card-title">格蘭路思享好禮</h2>
                  <p class="card-text mt-4">
                    現在正是收藏格蘭路思Whisky Maker's Cut的最好時機！因為之後它就要停產了！</br></br>
                    即日起入手格蘭路思Whisky Maker's Cut滿3瓶，即可獲得限量格蘭路思迷你酒樣品組1組，數量有限！
                  </p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-end mb-2 me-2 "><small class="text-muted">2024/01/23</small></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 消息3 -->
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="card mx-5">
            <div class="row g-1">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <a class="enlarge-img" href="/images/index/news/202401_03.png" title="春節營業時間">
                  <img src="/images/index/news/202401_03.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="春節營業時間">
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h2 class="card-title">梅乃宿青龍白虎</h2>
                  <p class="card-text mt-4">
                    過年歡聚不能少的就是山珍海味🍲🦐助興清酒更是不可缺席！</br></br>
                    帶上「左青龍、右白虎」坐鎮，讓您今年慶團圓美味特別加乘！
                  </p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-end mb-2 me-2 "><small class="text-muted">2024/01/26</small></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 控制器 -->
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#newsCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon bg-dark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#newsCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon bg-dark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
  </section>

